Aaron, for himself and the people; [Lev
9:8](../../../bib/kjv/lev009.htm#008.md), The sin offering, [Lev
9:12](../../../bib/kjv/lev009.htm#012.md), and the burnt offering for
himself; [Lev 9:15](../../../bib/kjv/lev009.htm#015.md), The offerings for
the people; [Lev 9:23](../../../bib/kjv/lev009.htm#023.md), Moses and Aaron
bless the people; [Lev 9:24](../../../bib/kjv/lev009.htm#024.md), Fire
comes from the Lord, upon the altar.

